WEBVTT

00:01.100 --> 00:03.700
Looks pretty tempting,
doesn't it?

00:03.700 --> 00:05.700
But what if I told you
that each one of these

00:05.700 --> 00:10.200
delicious little morsels
has almost a thousand calories?

00:10.200 --> 00:12.800
Would it make you
want one any less?

00:12.800 --> 00:16.100
Me, neither.
And that's normal.

00:21.200 --> 00:24.900
We all want things
that we know are bad for us.

00:28.000 --> 00:32.600
Everyone has dangerous fascinations
and unhealthy fixations.

00:33.800 --> 00:37.300
Some of them are a little
harder to explain than others.

00:38.600 --> 00:41.900
But most us know how
to keep our impulses in check.

00:41.900 --> 00:45.800
We use willpower to fight off
our darker instincts.

00:47.200 --> 00:50.400
Unfortunately, for others,

00:50.400 --> 00:53.400
willpower just isn't enough.

00:54.300 --> 00:57.400
The siren call
of one's own obsessions

00:57.400 --> 01:01.200
is simply too strong to resist.

