01:11.000 --> 01:14.000
The thing we used to want...

01:15.400 --> 01:18.300
...becomes the thing
we now need.

01:19.300 --> 01:22.900
Our obsession becomes
our compulsion.

01:24.100 --> 01:26.700
Until eventually we realize

01:26.700 --> 01:30.600
pursuing the one thing
we want most in life

01:31.600 --> 01:35.500
has left us without much
of a life at all.

01:36.600 --> 01:38.300
But in the end,

01:38.300 --> 01:41.700
our compulsions
are still there.

01:42.000 --> 01:45.800
Even after they've pushed us
to the brink of death,

01:46.500 --> 01:48.400
or guided us

01:48.400 --> 01:52.500
into places
of unimaginable horror.

01:58.400 --> 02:00.400
Okay. Don't be mad.

02:00.400 --> 02:03.000
I know, I know they're for that
bake sale at Bridgette's school,

02:03.000 --> 02:05.600
but what can I say?
I couldn't resist.

02:07.000 --> 02:09.400
- You want some?
- God, no.

02:09.400 --> 02:11.400
I'm going to bed.

02:11.400 --> 02:12.700
What?

02:12.700 --> 02:15.000
It was a cupcake.

